### Install is complete.  Standby as I tune it enough to get useful data.  
### Fine tuning the IDS is kind of a pain at first, since there are multiple input/outputs to modify.  
### Just remember to configure the base conf's, then the pulledpork.conf's, then perform all rule tuning in the rule files
### Fine tuning the engine itself will take you back to configuring the IDS' conf's
### there are white papers available for IDS engine tuning that I will provide here later.
